            <Briefcase className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Custom Lawyer Web Design</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Tailored websites that reflect your practice area and expertise—whether you're a family lawyer, criminal defense attorney, or estate planning specialist.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
