          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Mobile-Optimized Design</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Over 60% of legal searches happen on mobile. Your site looks flawless on every device.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-blue-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
