              <p class="text-black font-medium">Every element is designed to build trust and generate consultation requests.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-600 to-gray-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
                <path d="M2 12h20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
                <path d="M12 2c3 3 4.5 6.5 4.5 10S15 19 12 22c-3-3-4.5-6.5-4.5-10S9 5 12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Local SEO Expertise</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">I optimize for "lawyer near me" and practice-specific searches in your area.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Award className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Professional & Credible</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Your website reflects your reputation and expertise.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-600 to-gray-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Clock className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Quick Turnaround</h3>
